<h2 style="color: #CC0000">The Park Hotel</h2>   
Location: Located on the popular MG Road, The Park is rated among some of the finest 5 star boutique hotels in Bangalore. The Park, Bangalore is situated at a distance of 37.3 km from Kempegowda International Airport and 8.2 kms from Bangalore City Railway Station. Room Amenities.

It Offers 109 Luxuriously Furnished Rooms that are perfectly designed and crafted as per the taste of guests to make their stay relaxing and comfortable. The Rooms have been divided into several Categories, i.e., Deluxe (238 sqft 38 rooms), Deluxe Balcony (294 sqft 50 rooms) and Luxury Terrace (550 sqft 16 rooms). Each of these rooms includes facilities like mini bar, LCD, TV , Electronic Safe, Direct Dial Telephone, Hair Dryer and en- suite bathroom with modern fixtures.

Hotel Facilities: The Park Bangalore has well-furnished banquet halls which are apt for hosting parties, conferences, events and meetings. In order to ensure a delightful stay for guests, there are facilities like swimming pool, gymnasium, spa and gift shop. Additionally airport transfer, Wi-Fi access and travel desk are also offered by the hotel.

Dining: With multiple dining options, the hotel ensures foodies are delighted by the offerings. Monsoon, the 24-hour restaurant, serves Pan Indian and International cuisines. Acclaimed to be one of the best Italian restaurants in the country, Italia is another award-winning restaurant. i-Bar offers a wide selection of beverages. To relax, visit Aqua, a chic lounge by the pool. During the stay, don't miss a visit to the Aura, a spa that allows indulgence in a variety of treatment rooms. 


<h2 style="color: #CC0000">Hotel Ashwini Lodge</h2>
Located in Mysore, Hotel Ashwini Lodge is 500 m from Mysore Palace and Mysore Zoo. Brindavan Garden is 15 km from the property. Free private parking is available on site.

All units feature a TV. Every unit has a private bathroom with a bath. Towels and bed linen are offered.

Hotel Ashwini Lodge also includes a children's playground. Guests can enjoy a meal at the on-site restaurant. The property also offers packed lunches. Room service is available.

Dodda Gadiyara is 600 m from Hotel Ashwini Lodge.

This is our guests' favourite part of Mysore, according to independent reviews.

<h2 style="color: #CC0000">Accord Highland Hotel Ooty</h2>

Overlooking the beautiful Nilgiris Mountains, the hotel stands tall with all elegance and style. A contemporary structure with a traditional feel, Highland Hotel Ooty is one of India's most popular hills 5 Star Hotel, located at 2640 meters above sea level in the Nilgiris Hills of southern India. The brand new hotel is designed for maximum comfort loaded with LCD’s, Wi-Fi , direct dial phones,safe deposit lockers, in room Iron & iron board, Tea/ Coffee maker & a mini bar. Some other services provided by the hotel are 24-hour room service,, laundry service, purified water, Travel Desk, Business Centre ,valet service, doctor on call, foreign exchange facility etc.

<h2 style="color: #CC0000">Octave Plaza Hotel</h2>
Conveniently set in the Basavanagudi district of Bangalore, Octave Plaza Hotel is located less than 1 km from Bull Temple, 5 km from Kanteerava Indoor Stadium and 6 km from Visvesvaraya Industrial and Technological Museum. This 3-star hotel offers a 24-hour front desk and luggage storage space. The air-conditioned rooms provide a city view and come with a wardrobe and free WiFi.

At the hotel, each room includes a desk, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom.

Guests at Octave Plaza Hotel can enjoy a à la carte breakfast.

Forum Mall, Koramangala is 6 km from the accommodation, while Cubbon Park is 6 km away. The nearest airport is Kempegowda International, 40 km from Octave Plaza Hotel, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service.
      
